commit_message: Add notebook for generating fROH plots across cohorts
Create plots of population size and sequencing
Split out rules related to subsetting samples

Better parallelize gVCFs, chromosome.list changes, other fixes

- Simplify obtaining list of chromosomes
- Move chromosomes.list and create on first run
- Revert some uses of genocat that were not working
- Fix read groups for alignment
- gVCF creation is now split by chromosome
Split alignment rules into separate file

Move filtering to config, fix BAM RG

- Hard filtering is now read from config file
- BAM RG field now pulls the sample name from the run name

Coverage rules and plots

- Apply batch grouping to coverage rules
- New rules determining exon coverage
- Plot overall coverage across chromosomes
- Plot exome coverage across batches

Modify structural_variants.smk

- Split rules related to plotting alignments into own file
- Using process substitution `<(...)` to stop writing merged BAMs to disk
- SV calling consensus using SURVIVOR
Add --configfile option to README, rare variant tests
Add config to command and script for summarizing samples

Introduce ability to take into account data from different batches

- New config variable for determining whether runs from different batches should be treated as same sample
- Add batch to results path for `alignments/` and `trimmed/`
- Change `recalibrated/recal_tables/` to `recal_tables/`
Use sample run instead of organism ID
Improve SV processing and plot SVs
Divergence and expected heterozygosity with plots
Process WES and WGS separately during imputation
Add admixture rules, mask discordant regions
Plot heatmap for rate of inheritance of haplotypes
Cleanup unused code, filter and phasing changes
Remove markdup for AMP and GBS
Cut adapters for AMP, improve README.md
Cut adapters for GBS, move index rules to new file

Genotype refinement and haplotype estimation

New method to adjust genotype calls using trios and
population info, followed by haplotype estimation using SHAPEIT4.
Finish cutting adapters and keep "./." genotypes
Add pedigree info, create admixture graph
Modify admixture and create .fai index for GATK
Create rule for adding read groups
